import React, { Component } from 'react' import api from '../services/api' class Company extends Component { state = { name: '', address: '', cpfCnpj: '', telephone: '', images: '', show: false, loader: true } async handleDados(){ const id = localStorage.getItem('@Coliseu') const dados = await api.get(`/auth/company/${id}`) console.log(dados.data) this.setState({ name: dados.name, address: dados.address, cpfCnpj: dados.cpfCnpj, telephone: dados.telephone, images: dados.data.images[0].url }) return } componentDidMount() { this.handleDados() setTimeout(() =>{ this.setState({ show: true , loader: false }) },3000) } handleChange = e => { this.setState({[e.target.name]: e.target.value}) } render() { return (
